text: Armen Arslanian (9 July 1960 - 18 May 2015) was a Lebanese cyclist. He competed in the individual road race at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Lebanese male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Lebanon Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
